Text:
Hey, Mr DJ ! Looking for a powerful and easy-to-use MP3 DJ mix software ? You found it !

AtomixMP3 is the sharpest MP3 DJ mix software ever, providing one-click BPM beat matching, beat-aware loop engine, live recording, optional dual soundcard output and master tempo functionality.

AtomixMP3 supports skins and plugins. AtomixMP3 is designed for Windows 95/98/ME/NT/2000/XP  ....AtomixMP3 is only $ 59.95,

http://www.atomixmp3.com/
Vill inte låta gnällig eller otacksam på någotvis men regeln är väl att man seedar det man lägger upp.
